ca.mcgill.hs.classifiers.location
Class SignificantLocationClusterer

java.lang.Object
  ca.mcgill.hs.classifiers.location.SignificantLocationClusterer

public class SignificantLocationClusterer
extends java.lang.Object

This class clusters a set of locations, which are really points at which the user was stationary for a brief period of time, into places where the user visits regularly.
